nodes.text: Leary was a group of Lambda-class T-4a shuttles sent to capture Alpha-class Xg-1 Star Wings from an Imperial Outpost. Keyan Farlander guarded the operation and destroyed three Imperial shuttles sent in after disabling the gunboats.
The Mon Calamari Star Cruiser Cathleen would then arrive to retrieve the gunboats and Leary.
